The monthly publication of the comic ''Angel's Friends'' by [[Play Press]] began in March 2007. The printed version was edited by [[Red Whale]] and [[Yellow Whale]], scripted by [[Bruno Enna]] and drawn by [[Giada Perissinotto]]. The publication was discontinued in January 2008 with the release of Chapter 14, ''A Spark in the Heart''.

A second version of the comic, based on the cartoon, was published bimonthly by [[Giochi Preziosi|Preziosi Collection]] since 2009, in ''Angel's Friends Magazine''.<ref>{{cite news|language=Italian |url=http://www.preziosicollection.com/on-line/Home/Publishing/Archiviopubblicazioni2009/scheda1617.html |title=Angel's Friends Magazine N°1 |year=2009 |accessdate=30 January 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120814044349/http://www.preziosicollection.com/on-line/Home/Publishing/Archiviopubblicazioni2009/scheda1617.html |archivedate=14 August 2012 }}</ref> It was discontinued after the release of No. 4.

